  <description><![CDATA[<p>Pack your comfiest walking boots and get ready for a trekking adventure! The UNESCO listed <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/liguria/monterosso-cinque-terre">Cinque Terre</a> has some of the most famous and picturesque walks in Italy. We’ve planned a week long self-guided tour so that you to explore the villages at your own pace. With walking maps and transport included, you can relax as you take in the scenery, knowing that all the details are taken care of.</p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/trekking-the-cinque-terre-self-guided-tour">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/trekking-the-cinque-terre-self-guided-tour">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/trekking-the-cinque-terre-self-guided-tour">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/trekking-the-cinque-terre-self-guided-tour">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/trekking-the-cinque-terre-self-guided-tour">Departure dates</a></h2>
